text: Falsamblesthis seriepilosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Theodor Franz Wilhelm Kirsch in 1889. It is known from Ecuador."Falsamblesthis seriepilosa (Kirsch, 1889)". BioLib. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1889
